MVC with Observer pattern for pygtk2
=====
Author: Roberto Cavada <cavada AT fbk.eu>

In 2010 Tobias Weber <towb AT celvina.de> has joined the development
"team".


New Versions
============
New versions of this package can be found at:
 <http://pygtkmvc.sourceforge.net>


